# temp-game-hub

## Stack
- Next.js 16, TypeScript, Tailwind v4
- Prisma + SQLite
- Vitest for tests

## Structure
- src/app/games/ — game pages
- src/lib/games/ — game logic, keep separate from pages
- public/ — static assets including words.json and nyt-answers.json

## Conventions
- Game logic stays in src/lib, never in page.tsx
- Pages only import from lib, no logic duplication
- Use "use client" at top of all game pages
- Do not modify wordle-solver.ts and page.tsx in the same task
- Always show me the full file contents when making changes to any file
